---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base title="About the Editor - The Windy Times">
  <article class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="headline-md mb-4">About the Editor — Michael Perkins</h2>
      <div class="overflow-hidden">
        <img
          src="/michael-perkins.jpg"
          alt="Michael Perkins"
          class="w-[250px] h-[250px] rounded-lg object-cover float-right ml-6 mb-4"
        />
        <p class="summary">
          I'm an energy industry expert who's worked in the wind energy sector in Australia for 15 years. I'm a passionate advocate for action on climate change, but in my heart I'm an engineer and a pragmatist looking for practical solutions to power the world.
        </p>
        <p class="summary mt-4">
          I created The Windy Times to help others stay informed about what's happening in the Australian Wind Energy industry.
        </p>
        <p class="summary mt-4">
          You can find me on <a href="https://au.linkedin.com/in/michael-perkins-11b2a710b" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="link-blue">LinkedIn</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="headline-md mb-4">My Sources</h2>
      <p class="summary">
        I aggregate news from energy publications such as RenewEconomy, WattClarity, the AFR and PV Magazine Australia as well as industry sources such as the Clean Energy Council, EnergyCo and QREC.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="headline-md mb-4">How Content is Selected</h2>
      <p class="summary">
        Articles are curated using AI-assisted filtering to identify stories
        relevant to the Australian Wind Energy sector. Each article is reviewed
        for relevance before being published to this site.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="headline-md mb-4">Contact</h2>
      <p class="summary">
        For questions or feedback, contact me on <a href="https://au.linkedin.com/in/michael-perkins-11b2a710b" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="link-blue">LinkedIn</a>.
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>
</Base>
